  { textEs: 'El que tenga sed, venga; y el que quiera, tome gratuitamente del agua de la vida.', textEn: 'Let the one who is thirsty come; and let the one who wishes take the free gift of the water of life.', referenceEs: 'Apocalipsis 22:17', referenceEn: 'Revelation 22:17' }
